      "content": "That's an interesting perspective. When you talk about \"dilution\" and \"clashing norms,\" are you implying that these demographic changes are inherently destabilizing because these groups might not share the same fundamental commitment to our political systems? Like, is there a specific risk that these cultural shifts will naturally make the country harder to govern or more prone to chaos?",
